<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note70" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Diodorus_Siculus/18A*.html#ref70
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">70</A>
According to Pausanias
	<A HREF="
https://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus:text:1999.01.0160:book=2:chapter=33
	"TARGET="offsite"
